        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 3:20",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). This Maachah was the favorite wife of Rehoboam ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 11:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and the mother of Abijam. The way in which she is here mentioned strongly favors the notion that the position of queen-mother was a definite one at the court, and could only be held by one person at a time. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
